<br>
Some of you missed my point.  <br>
<br>
Epic Pet- LVL 49 4000+ HP<br>
Lvl57-60 Pet - LVL 48 3500+- HP<br>
Lvl 51-54 Pet - LVL 45 ? HP (correct me if I'm wrong)<br>
<br>
There's only one level difference between epic and regular pets.  What lvl are you gonna put our new PoP pets?  I'm sure VI will not make a level called 48.5 to make it less than epic.<br>
<br>
Our pets have been scaling up with our levels.  There's no reason why regular 61-65 pets being a higher level than a lvl 49 epic pet.  Our level 61-65 pets should be at LEAST level 51+.  History tells us that higher the lvl, stronger they are.  In result, pet should be stronger than current epic.<br>
<br>
Yes, people worked hard for epic and it will be sad when it gets over powerd by new 61+ pets.  To award those epiced people, VI should created add on epic quests for epiced people, not only mages but for all classes.<br>
<br>
For people who are asking focus items...  there's already a focus item in VT (a glove) to make epic pet and 57-60 pets stronger.<br>
<br>
Conclusion:<br>
1.  In order to scale with PoP level of play, new pets should be stronger than current epic.  Level 49(epic) pet will not stand a chance agains PoP mobs.<br>
2.  VI should prepare Add-on epic quests (for all classes) to make current epic stronger than PoP pets.<br>
<br>
Cavashan<br>
